# Trivy ignore list — suppressed image vulnerabilities.
#
# The Docker CI job fails on any CRITICAL CVE. To suppress a finding, add its
# CVE ID below WITH a justification comment and (ideally) an expiry date.
# Unjustified suppressions are rejected in review (see ISSUE 2.6).
#
# Format:
#   CVE-2024-XXXXX  # justification — owner — review-by YYYY-MM-DD
#
# (no suppressions yet)
